Value Required,Filldown SERVICE_NAME (\S(?:.*\S)?)
Value Required PROTOCOL (Any|TCP|UDP|ICMP|IPv6-ICMP|GRE|ESP|AH|IPv4|IPv6|OSPFIGP|IP)
Value DST_PORT (\S+)
Value SRC_PORT (\S+|-)
Value TIMEOUT (-)

Start
  ^.*Name\s+Protocol\s+Dst-Port/Type.* -> Continue
  ^\s*Total configured:.* -> Continue
  ^\s*$$ -> Continue
  ^\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${DST_PORT}\s+${SRC_PORT}\s*${TIMEOUT}? -> Continue.Record
  ^${SERVICE_NAME}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${DST_PORT}\s+${SRC_PORT}\s*${TIMEOUT}? -> Continue.Record